  "description": {
    "zh": "小伙子。我需要你的帮助。\n\n我们从兽医诊所和X光办公室获取的信息不够完整。我们的下一个目标是药店。市区有好几家，所以我觉得那些盗贼不会一次性偷走所有东西。帮我去那些药店踩点，然后我派人去收集东西。我知道的至少就有三家。去看看现在是什么情况。",
    "en": "Hello, young man. I need your help.\n\nWhat we found at the vet clinic and the x-ray office was not enough. Our next target is pharmacies. There were plenty of them around the city, so I don't think the thieves had time to take everything. Check out the pharmacies for me, then I'll send my men over. I know of at least three. See what condition they're in."
  },
